            <h3>I. Explain the code in the main.hbs</h3>
            <p>
                The main.hbs file is a handlebars template that defines the layout for our website. It consists of several sections:
            </p>
            <p>
                The <strong>Header</strong> contains the website logo and navigation menu. It helps users identify the website and provides easy access to various pages.
